race.comment: MY SWEETHEART (4) stepped out for the first time last start and was just fair in finishing eighth at Gosford over 1200m, beaten 7 lengths. Watch for a much better performance this time. HUTT STREET (5) faded late last time over 1400m at Orange after showing good early speed, eventually finishing fourth. Will take catching. MEGAPHONE MISS (7) was in the money two starts back at Warren but was unable to repeat the effort last time when sixth, beaten 6 lengths, at Narromine over 1100m. Tackling a more suitable race this time so she is likely to play a big role. SNOWBALL (10) was in the money two starts back at Narromine but couldn't back it up last time when seventh, beaten 3.5 lengths, at Tamworth over 1000m. Looks well placed so expect a better run this time.
